    4. Complete the prejudging for " transform="translate(0 404)" fill="#202124" font-size="18" font-family="Raleway-Regular, Raleway"><tspan x="0" y="17">1 .Select </tspan><tspan y="17" font-family="Raleway-Bold, Raleway" font-weight="700">My Judging Categories</tspan><tspan y="17" xml:space="preserve"> to review the categories you have been assigned</tspan><tspan x="0" y="43">2. Each page has a short description of each piece. </tspan><tspan x="0" y="69">3. Click on the description to select the entry. This will take you to the first question. </tspan><tspan x="0" y="95">4. Complete the prejudging for the entry by selecting the appropriate radio button.</tspan><tspan x="0" y="121">5. When finished hit the submit button.</tspan><tspan x="0" y="147">6. Complete a questionnaire for each entry in every category you have been assigned.</tspan><tspan x="0" y="173" xml:space="preserve">7.  Once complete you can go to the results page and see all of your scores.  </tspan><tspan x="0" y="199" xml:space="preserve">8. On  the day of judging bring your notes to review with your team. </tspan><tspan x="0" y="225">9. Once the final winners are decided, the group leader should go to the</tspan><tspan y="225" xml:space="preserve" font-family="Raleway-Bold, Raleway" font-weight="700"> Award Winners</tspan><tspan y="225" xml:space="preserve"> tab to </tspan><tspan x="0" y="251" xml:space="preserve">    enter the winners.</tspan><tspan x="0" y="277"></tspan><tspan x="0" y="303"></tspan><tspan x="0" y="329">• More than one &quot;Award of Merit&quot; or &quot;Award of Excellence&quot; can be awarded if there are entries that </tspan><tspan x="0" y="355" xml:space="preserve">  deserve it.</tspan><tspan x="0" y="381">• Please come with your phone or device to view and enter your results.</tspan></text>
